description.p:
BET specific surface: 223 m2 /g


pore volume: 1.2 cm3 /g (for pore radii of between 40  Angstrom  and 63 microns);


sodium content: 900 ppm.

Furthermore, two separate aqueous solutions are prepared:


a chromium trioxide (CrO3) solution to which nickel chloride hexahydrate has been added;


a methanolic solution containing 3 to 4.5 molar equivalents of methanol per mole of chromium.
